name: Henry Walsh
content:
It didn't reinvent the wheel. It didn't look at the comics and say, "Feh, this is dumb. Let me change all of this because I can do it better."

#Shazam said, "I'm based on a comic book! Let's do this!"

From exclamations of, "Holy moley!" To "Shazam!" They took it seriously...
